---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - OurCouple" description="OurCouple Terms of Service: Rules for using our private couple app. Free to use, premium features available. Must be 16+ to use." canonicalPath="/terms">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-gradient-radial">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="OurCouple" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl" />
        <span class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-text">OurCouple</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-1 pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">Last updated: January 21, 2026</p>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            By downloading, installing, or using OurCouple ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the App.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            These Terms also apply to our website and waitlist registration.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">2. Eligibility</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            You must be at least 16 years old to use OurCouple. By using the App, you represent and warrant that you meet this age requirement.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">3. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple is a private couples app that allows partners to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Share daily manifestations (messages and photos)</li>
            <li>Save and share inspirational quotes and messages</li>
            <li>Capture and store shared moments and memories</li>
            <li>Create shared notes and lists</li>
            <li>Track important events and dates with reminders</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            The App is intended for personal, non-commercial use only between two consenting people in a relationship.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">4. Account Registration</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            To use the App, you must create an account. You agree to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized access</li>
            <li>Be responsible for all activities under your account</li>
            <li>Not share your account with anyone other than your connected partner</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">5. Partner Connection</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple allows you to connect with one partner. By inviting or accepting a partner connection, you acknowledge and agree that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Your shared content will be visible to your connected partner</li>
            <li>You have the consent of the person you are inviting</li>
            <li>You will not use this feature to harass or monitor anyone without their knowledge</li>
            <li>Either partner can disconnect at any time</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">6. User Content</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            You retain full ownership of all content you create or upload to the App. By using the App, you grant us a limited, non-exclusive license to store, process, and display your content solely for the purpose of providing our services to you and your partner.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            You agree not to upload content that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Is illegal, harmful, threatening, or offensive</li>
            <li>Depicts minors inappropriately</li>
            <li>Infringes on others' intellectual property or privacy rights</li>
            <li>Contains malicious code, viruses, or harmful software</li>
            <li>Violates any applicable laws or regulations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            We do not monitor or review your content, but we reserve the right to remove content that violates these Terms if brought to our attention.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">7. Premium Subscription</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple may offer a premium subscription with additional features. By subscribing, you agree to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Pay the applicable fees through the Apple App Store or Google Play Store</li>
            <li>Automatic renewal unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the renewal date</li>
            <li>Manage and cancel subscriptions through your device's app store settings</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            Prices may vary by region and are subject to change. Refunds are handled according to Apple App Store or Google Play Store policies. We do not process payments directly.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">8. Privacy & Encryption</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Your privacy is important to us. Please review our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">Privacy Policy</a> to understand how we collect, use, and protect your information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple uses <strong>encryption</strong> to protect your personal content. This means:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Your messages, photos, notes, and moments are encrypted on your device</li>
            <li>Only you and your partner can decrypt this content</li>
            <li>We cannot access, read, or recover your encrypted data</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            <strong>Important:</strong> Because of E2EE, if you lose access to your account and cannot recover your password, your encrypted content cannot be recovered. You are responsible for maintaining access to your account.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">9. Prohibited Conduct</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            You agree not to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Use the App for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or other users' accounts</li>
            <li>Interfere with or disrupt the App's functionality or servers</li>
            <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the App</li>
            <li>Use the App to harass, stalk, abuse, or harm others</li>
            <li>Create multiple accounts or use the App if previously banned</li>
            <li>Use automated systems or bots to access the App</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">10. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            The App, including its design, features, code, and branding, is owned by OurCouple and protected by intellectual property laws. You may not copy, modify, distribute, or create derivative works based on the App without our written permission.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">11. Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account at any time for violation of these Terms, without prior notice. You may delete your account at any time through the App settings.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Upon termination, your right to use the App ceases immediately. Your data will be deleted according to our Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">12. Disclaimers</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            The App is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not guarantee that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>The App will be error-free or uninterrupted</li>
            <li>Any errors will be corrected</li>
            <li>The App will meet your specific requirements</li>
            <li>Encrypted data can be recovered if you lose access to your account</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            We recommend keeping backups of important content. Due to our encryption, we cannot recover your encrypted data if you lose access to your account. We are not responsible for any loss of data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">13. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, OurCouple and its operators shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to loss of data, profits, or goodwill, arising from your use of the App.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Our total liability for any claims related to the App shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the 12 months preceding the claim, or ‚Ç¨50, whichever is greater.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">14. Indemnification</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless OurCouple from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from your use of the App, your violation of these Terms, or your violation of any rights of others.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">15. Governing Law & Disputes</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            These Terms are governed by the laws of France, without regard to conflict of law principles. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the App shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Paris, France.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            If you are a consumer in the European Union, you retain any mandatory protections provided by the laws of your country of residence.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">16. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify you of material changes by posting a notice in the App or sending an email. Continued use of the App after such notice constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">17. Severability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            If any provision of these Terms is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision shall be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary, and the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">18. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            For questions about these Terms, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium">
            <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev">contact@vynse.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors font-medium">
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-card border-t border-border py-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-text-light text-sm">
